title: Audiosurf 2 Beta - 30/12/2013 Update ~Kaise123
description:
Audiosurf 2 (December 30th 2013 Update)

Changes:
Fixed: Added a couple extra seconds of track at the end of the song to allow matches time to clear. 
Fixed: Alt+TAB now works correctly in fullscreen 
Fixed: Song selector now returns to your previous position (as it did weeks ago) 
Updated: game engine and in-game web browser to latest versions. 

Uploaded by Kaise123. Crack origin unknown, Taken from previous Audiosurf torrent and used on the latest update from Steam.
